{
  "stem": "22734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- he left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then he-- he said, you will all be sent away anyway, and I'll took this apartment over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's just the right kind of apartment for me and my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we are in a small apartment across the hall from you, and we won't stay there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the people started to get notices who lived with us to go into the transport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then there was another-- they-- and they called the guys who-- who did this attempt at on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were hiding in a basement in a church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And somebody denounced them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they-- they-- so many-- thousands of people lost their lives because of this one man who was really terrible, when you-- historically when you look at him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was a terrible figure but-- it cost too much-- too many lives were paid for this one person.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyhow, in-- in October we got-- until then, we were supposedly protected, my mother and I, because my father was in jail in Prague.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they didn't like to-- it was their crazy idea that families shouldn't be separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he-- we were in a way protected from the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But only until a certain point because then there was another penalty transport-- I forget for what-- we were called in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Rudolf ?] wasn't and his parents weren't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were desperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he found out from some of his friends that this is a penalty transport which will stop in Terezin for a day but nobody will be allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they will go-- they will all go east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went to the Gestapo and said that I was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that he wants to go with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
